# Exclude Claude-derived development files from source archives (git archive,
# GitHub release tarball, Zenodo snapshot). Keeps them in the repo but off any
# published source distribution. Mirrors the MANIFEST.in prune set so the
# Zenodo tarball matches the PyPI sdist/wheel exclusions.
.claude/             export-ignore
.specify/            export-ignore
.planning/           export-ignore
specs/               export-ignore
docs/sessions/       export-ignore
docs/introspections/ export-ignore
CLAUDE.md            export-ignore
AGENTS.md            export-ignore
.domi-pin            export-ignore
